data.description:
MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED- DEADLINE DEC 1 AT 2P: Welcome to this superb property, an entertainment haven with an extensive 0.29-acre lot and limiless living with no HOA. The outdoor space is a dream, featuring a spacious patio, gas-heated pool, Jacuzzi, storage shed, yard so big has enough room for your RV parking.
Inside, elegant hardwood flooring in the living and dining areas creates an inviting atmosphere. The master bedroom offers a spacious California closet, and there's a versatile room for work or play. The kitchen is functional and stylish, with an inviting island and integrated indoor fireplace.
Note that the heated pool needs cleaning. Embrace limitless living with no HOA – schedule a showing today and make it yours! Swimming pool has a limited LIFETIME WARRANTY and this is uploaded here-in. House has very minor cracks and repair estimate is in TD. Cash or Conventional preferred.
